  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The biggest value of CRC cards is to allow people to break away from the procedural mode of thought and more fully&#xD;
    appreciate object technology. CRC Cards allow entire project teams to contribute to the design. The more people who can&#xD;
    help design the system&amp;nbsp;the greater the number of good ideas incorporated.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    Source: &lt;a&#xD;
    href=&quot;http://www.extremeprogramming.org/rules/crccards.html&quot;>http://www.extremeprogramming.org/rules/crccards.html&lt;/a>&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
